KG My skin is thick after all these years. I respect constructive criticism that is fact based. Glittering generalities, often from @realdonaldtrump base, that fail to be specific and use the words "inflammatory" etc are nonsensical. I respect free speech and hope is data driven.
Did @realdonaldtrump inaction cause the loss of lives and risk more virus related deaths ahead? Answer these questions.

As Grandma Koufax would say, "So be it." As I say opinions are like assholes everyone has one (and that includes me). I try to be facts based Ryan and I find that objections like yours are not data based but "one liners." Did @realdonaldtrump fail to understand the gravity?

Though I acknowledge that the strongest supports (his base) of @realdonaldtrump will be unmoved by his actions - if a few independent Republicans move away from him in Nov. because of my tweets (and others) I will consider it a job well done. This, to me, is my civic duty.

Hold on, I am not pushing hate. Listen to the interview Kernen/Trump that I tweeted out and make your own decision whether @realdonaldtrump is liable for his slow moving action. I have made mine - many others have as well. And the election is in November and not October.
